eate their own. While this is a critical constraint, the knowledge file already implies this indirectly, so I'll classify it as minor. My final assessment: all four issues are minor severity, with the main findings being the missing footnote about custom login implementation, the behavioral detail about exception message handling, the section numbering inconsistency, and the absent hints section. The configuration example also references several utility classes like SimpleDbTransactionManager, BasicSystemTimeProvider, and BasicBusinessDateProvider that should be included in the hints section but are currently missing.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":20022,"cache_read_input_tokens":18561,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":20022,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":8},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e7bd2ec6-c0a1-469d-b516-250c5a781ed7","uuid":"f6d663c9-8930-4fc5-8612-1df9c7b23368"}
